# Atlantis – The NW African Shelf Empire  
One Coherent, Fully Evidence-Compliant Reconstruction  
Locked: 5 December 2025 – Version 2.0  

## 1. Core Identification
- Royal capital & ceremonial centre: Richat Structure (Guelb er Richât), Mauritania  
  21.1240° N, 11.4016° W – the perfect natural concentric-ring city
- Empire territory: NW African continental shelf + Mauritanian-Adrar plateau at –120 m sea level  
  ≈ 1.9–2.1 million km²
- Original Pillars of Hercules: Volcanic island/ridge chain immediately east of the Atlas Mountains  
  (Seine Seamount, Josephine Seamount, Essaouira–Agadir ridge – emergent at –120 m)
- Modern Pillars: Name migrated to Strait of Gibraltar after the originals drowned

## 2. Primary Trigger – The 12 ka Solar-Geomagnetic-Impact Excursion Cycle
| Phase                              | Timing (ka BP) | Mechanism                                                                 | Effect on Atlantis |
|------------------------------------|----------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|-------------------|
| Galactic current-sheet crossing      | 14–13          | Cosmic-ray flux spike                                                      | Solar instability begins |
| Solar micronova proxy               | 13–12.9        | Extreme solar outburst                                                     | Atmospheric ionisation |
