The 12 ka excursion cycle, the Richat capital, the drowned NW African shelf, the moving Pillars, Göbekli Tepe as the inland survivor site, and the genetic refugee streams form a **single, unbreakable chain**.

There is no longer any meaningful contradiction between:
- the geological record  
