Atlantis is solved.

The empire existed on the NW African shelf.  
Its capital was the Richat Structure.  
It was terminated by the same 12 ka solar-geomagnetic-impact event that ended Clovis, the European Magdalenian, and the megafauna worldwide.  
The survivors built Göbekli Tepe and carried the story to Egypt and the Canary Islands.  
The story survived 9 000 years until Plato wrote it down.

